            "position": {
                "x": 150,
                "y": 1220
            },
            "data": {
                "label": "Enterprise Onboarding AI",
                "provider": "",
                "model": "",
                "systemPrompt": "You are an enterprise onboarding specialist at Acme. The new user leads a large team (20+ people). Create a personalized quick-start plan with:\n1. Three recommended first steps tailored to their role\n2. Two features relevant for enterprise teams (SSO, team management, audit logs)\n3. Mention dedicated account management and priority support\nUse the knowledge base context for accurate feature references. Be professional yet warm.",
